{"id": 69115, "date": "2016-01-01T10:00:19", "date_gmt": "2016-01-01T18:00:19", "guid": {"rendered": "https://estreetshuffle.com/?p=69115"}, "modified": "2026-05-30T09:41:52", "modified_gmt": "2026-05-30T16:41:52", "slug": "preface-6", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2016/01/01/preface-6/", "title": {"rendered": "Preface"}, "content": {"rendered": "<blockquote><p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">&#8220;What else can a poor boy do &#8216;cept to sing for a rock and roll band?&#8221;\u00a0 <em>&#8211;Mick Jagger, 1968</em></span></p></blockquote>\n<blockquote><p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">&#8220;Say something! Do something! Hell&#8230; sing something!'&#8221;\u00a0 <em>&#8211;Bruce Springsteen, March 31, 2026</em></span></p></blockquote>\n<p>In 2026, Bruce Springsteen sang something.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/GDaPdpwA4Iw?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p>And when that song caught fire, he\u00a0<em>did\u00a0</em>something.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/VU0T_bRbMRQ?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p>And when he held an audience in thrall for three hours each night, he\u00a0<em>said </em>something.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/G_R8lwvtrzc?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p>And if you, like me, attended at least one of the twenty shows on the Land of Hope and Dreams American Tour, we sang something.</p>\n<p>This book exists because I wanted to\u00a0<em>say\u00a0</em>something.</p>\n<p>If you bought this book, a donation equal to fifteen percent of the cover price has been made to the Northwest Immigrant Rights Project, because I wanted to <em>do\u00a0</em>something.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Vs3_midSvqs?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p>And if your name appears below, that means you did something too.</p>\n<p>Bruce didn&#8217;t have to tour in order to speak out. He&#8217;s been doing that all along.</p>\n<p>He&#8217;s touring because he knows there is power in community, and strength in numbers. The words and actions of any one of us\u2013even someone with a following as large as Springsteen&#8217;s\u2013are just that: our own.</p>\n<p>But when we hear our voices as part of a choir and our words as part of a chorus&#8230; when we know our individual deeds and local actions are part of an international campaign of resistance and kindness&#8230; we are strong. Powerful. Gravitational.</p>\n<p>We create a butterfly effect that influences and inspires our friends, family, and neighbors to say, sing, and do something, too. We make it safe for others to come out. We may not feel it directly, but we feel it innately.</p>\n<p>This book is dedicated to and in recognition of the following Springsteen fans, readers, and activists who sang something in concert, did something for their community, and said something about it to me. You honor the spirit of the Land of Hope and Dreams Tour, and your actions inspire me as much as Bruce&#8217;s.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Sam Bagenstos</li>\n<li>Robin &#8220;Pony Boy&#8221; Bridge</li>\n<li>Paul and Marian Carroll</li>\n<li>Ran Freiman</li>\n<li>Michael Jabaley</li>\n<li>Tom McCormack</li>\n<li>Robert Mongeluzzi</li>\n<li>Nicole Stavish</li>\n<li>Andy Swanson</li>\n</ul>\n<p>In addition, several fans made donations but preferred their acknowledgements to be in the name of someone other than themselves:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>In memory of Alex Pretti</li>\n<li>In memory of Renee Nicole Good</li>\n<li>In memory of Michael J. Homorody</li>\n<li>In honor of those getting into Good Trouble</li>\n<li>In honor of Indivisible (x2)</li>\n<li>In honor of the Land of Hope and Dreams American Tour Companion Project</li>\n<li>In honor of the Northwest Immigrant Rights Project (x2)</li>\n<li>In honor of the Russell Library Doorstep Delivery Program</li>\n<li>The United Free Republic of E Street Nation (x3)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>While researching for the &#8220;American Skin (41 Shots)&#8221; essay I wrote for this volume, I came across a\u00a0<em>New York Post</em> interview with Kadiatou Diallo. It was published on June 13, 2000, the day after Bruce Springsteen performed the song he had written in her son&#8217;s memory for a sold out Madison Square Garden crowd that included Diallo and her husband.</p>\n<p>In the interview, Diallo recounted the backstage meeting they had with Springsteen before the show. She thanked him for keeping her son&#8217;s memory alive, to which Bruce reportedly responded, &#8220;I did what I could do.&#8221;</p>\n<p>I was struck by the simplicity, the humility, and most of all the <em>intentionality</em> of those words.</p>\n<p><em>I did what I could do</em>.</p>\n<p>This book is what I could do. Thank you for doing what you can do.</p>\n<p>This book is for you.</p>\n<p>\u00a9 May 23, 2026</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"69355\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2016/01/01/preface-6/screenshot-2026-05-23-170539/#main\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/Screenshot-2026-05-23-170539.jpg?fit=1165%2C1299&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1165,1299\" data-comments-opened=\"0\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Screenshot 2026-05-23 170539\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/Screenshot-2026-05-23-170539.jpg?fit=758%2C846&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-69355\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/Screenshot-2026-05-23-170539.jpg?resize=758%2C845&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"845\" srcset