gust 3, 1988", "format": false, "excerpt": "\"Dustland Fairytale\" was always a Springsteen song in spirit. It had the cinematic scale, the desperate romanticism, and that specific brand of \"get-out-while-we\u2019re-young\" energy. But it was wrapped in the velvet and glitter of 21st-century indie rock. It was a tribute from a distance. https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-3hyrkzFRss&pp=ygUQa2lsbGVycyBkdXN0bGFuZA%3D%3D Until it wasn't. In the\u2026", "rel": "", "context": "In &quot;Great&quot;", "block_context": {"text": "Great", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/category/great/"}, "img": {"alt_text": "", "src": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/The-Killers-Springsteen-1e53407108a047e7ad74fc6295ad0238.jpg?fit=1200%2C664&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200", "width": 350, "height": 200, "srcset": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/The-Killers-Springsteen-1e53407108a047e7ad74fc6295ad0238.jpg?fit=1200%2C664&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200 1x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/The-Killers-Springsteen-1e53407108a047e7ad74fc6295ad0238.jpg?fit=1200%2C664&ssl=1&resize=525%2C300 1.5x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/The-Killers-Springsteen-1e53407108a047e7ad74fc6295ad0238.jpg?fit=1200%2C664&ssl=1&resize=700%2C400 2x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/The-Killers-Springsteen-1e53407108a047e7ad74fc6295ad0238.jpg?fit=1200%2C664&ssl=1&resize=1050%2C600 3x"}, "classes": []}, {"id": 56834, "url": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/05/23/kingdom-of-days-may-23-2/", "url_meta": {"origin": 69115, "position": 4}, "title": "May 23", "author": "Ken", "date": "May 23, 2025", "format": false, "excerpt": "On this date: The legendary Darkness on the Edge of Town Tour begins! Hear the soundcheck and opening inside, and watch tour premieres and rarities galore from this date in history.", "rel": "", "context": "In &quot;Kingdom of Days&quot;", "bl